WEBVTT

00:00:00.444 --> 00:00:02.365
Track 09.04

00:00:04.152 --> 00:00:04.986
Narrator: 1

00:00:06.454 --> 00:00:12.413
A: It’s –7°C! I don’t like winter!

00:00:12.915 --> 00:00:16.563
B: Really? I like this season.

00:00:16.749 --> 00:00:22.216
I like cold weather and I really like snow!

00:00:23.778 --> 00:00:24.598
Narrator: 2

00:00:25.855 --> 00:00:28.513
A: It’s really windy today.

00:00:29.241 --> 00:00:30.113
B: Yes,

00:00:30.405 --> 00:00:33.236
there’s always a lot of wind in the autumn.

00:00:34.984 --> 00:00:35.949
Narrator: 3

00:00:37.047 --> 00:00:39.494
A: Look at the rain!

00:00:39.693 --> 00:00:43.026
B: I know. It often rains in this country.

00:00:44.790 --> 00:00:45.650
Narrator: 4

00:00:46.893 --> 00:00:49.724
A: Did you have good weather on holiday?

00:00:50.055 --> 00:00:53.758
It was 42°C here.

00:00:53.890 --> 00:00:59.815
B: 42°C! It wasn’t hot,

00:00:59.966 --> 00:01:02.982
but it was warm and sunny every day.